metadata.name: Monday Gm !
metadata.description:
One Gm a day keeps the devil away! 🔥  
An open edition piece to honor each day of the week, as each one is a new and colorful experience with the Gm cult. Grab one and say Gm, it makes the day so much brighter!  🍀☀️❤️‍🔥 
7 pieces for the 7 days, Let’s Celebrate!  

Good Morniiin'! 😇🫶👑
